==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: prescriptivist
<hw>pre*scrip"tiv*ist</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A person who
believes that acceptable practices should be prescribed by an authority
rather than be determined by the usage of the general public;
especially, a supporter of prescriptive{2} rules of grammar; -- also
used attributively, as <ex>prescriptivist</ex> grammar.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Prescriptively</ent>⟦br⟧
